@ {-Rise-of-the-Truth-}

This divx is obviously ripped from the usually low-quality Serbian DVD release - http://www.yu4you.com/items/sr/dvd/item_1.html

The copy shown at Croatian TV was new transfer from the original negative - Croatian Television is usually screening domestic movies from from its own new transfers done directly from the stocks of Croatian Cinematheque. The quality is always much better than DVD release.
